fr.sylfrey.misTiGriD.temperature.impl

Class WallImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.sylfrey.misTiGriD.temperature.impl.WallImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Opening, Wall

    public class WallImpl
extends Object
implements Wall, Opening
    A physical wall that separates rooms in a house, or a room and the external atmosphere. This wall features an opening by default, for instance a door or window; the opening state (open/closed) changes the wall's heat conductance.
    Author:
    syl
